lead_paragraph: Not long ago Brooke Henderson was simply trying to make ends meet as a rookie on the LPGA Tour but fast forward 18 months and she is breathing down the neck of Lydia Ko at the top of the world rankings.

headline.print_headline: Henderson Says Rise to Second in World Is 'Surreal'
headline.main: Henderson Says Rise to Second in World Is 'Surreal'
